                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18450407-980-offence-1 t18450407-cd-85"></join>5th of April</rs>, 1 mare, price 2<hi rend="italic">l</hi>., the property of <persName id="t18450407-name-1089" type="victimName">
