                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined by</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. DOANE</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> You were on duty at the toll-gate in uniform? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Yes.</p>
